1995-06-01|1996-12-30.description: The Man of Muscle Mystery survives his passage through the transporter tube, a baptism of blood that places him in the secret base of the Legion of Legions, there to meet the leader of Faculty X. And out of the endless chaos, the Singer's consciousness returns, where he finds himself in the most unexpected place.

1995-06-01|1996-12-30.description: The Saint of Killers is born and goes about his terrible business. He curses himself by intentionally murdering innocents.

1995-06-01|1996-12-30.description: Luke Skywalker's Jedi senses have been struck blind! To make matters worse, Grand Admiral Thrawn has just arranged to receive a shipment of creatures capable of pushing back the power of the Force. Thrawns's purpose: to ambush Luke and turn him over to the dark Jedi Master, Joruus C'baoth!

1995-06-01|1996-12-30.description: It used to be that China's worst problem was collecting rent from eccentric inventor Dr. Breckenridge and his young assistant -- and her secret love -- Jim. But now that the pair have vanished completely, China's biggest problem is her broken heart. Maybe she shouldn't have been so insistent on their paying? Maybe she shouldn't have gotten drunk and ordered them to leave? All the "maybes" in the world won't get Jim back, so China will have to take another course of action.
